{"tid":54802,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"為何一直比我假希望？","createTime":"2016-12-25T22:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T22:59:50.000Z","uid":3799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f89451366c7da2c745a5fa456d4f4ef103005c3d","tid":54802,"uid":3799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T22:22:19.000Z","msg":"分咗手一嗰星期,因為大家係同事<br />\n所以keep住聯絡<br />\n琴日佢話我知佢腸胃炎,我就話收工買粥,麵包上佢屋企<br />\n上到去佢屋企,我見到佢間房,仲掛住咗我地嘅合照<br />\n但都係唔願意復合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n那為何要比我假希望<br />\n點解要比我上你屋企照顧你？<br />\n<br />\n分手原因:佢話大家好似變咗屋企人,無咗情侶嘅感覺<br />\n唔想再濫用我對佢嘅好 繼續扮愛我"},{"pid":"11b3594cc6f4d325e0a4db71a77102bbc42201ce","tid":54802,"uid":14080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T22:25:57.000Z","msg":"又係啲on9藉口，早走早著啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99d76d3672f20e40f580a5999b270b961f947c5","tid":54802,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T22:29:00.000Z","msg":"愛情係咁咖喎<br />\n好難keep住一直有愛情<br />\n耐咗就會變親情"},{"pid":"71b0f29f2130b64ec0fe5ee10121472a457672ae","tid":54802,"uid":3799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T22:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛情係咁咖喎<br />\n好難keep住一直有愛情<br />\n耐咗就會變親情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同佢都係21歲,佢話我知 佢未玩夠"},{"pid":"28c9ddb763fbb3135abd7b7bd4b477b44a5a5247","tid":54802,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T22:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>愛情係咁咖喎<br />\n好難keep住一直有愛情<br />\n耐咗就會變親情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同佢都係21歲,佢話我知 佢未玩夠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁得啦 應該有第三者"},{"pid":"f02d85712224b19b590cfa56b54d1942cad11b6d","tid":54802,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T22:34:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>愛情係咁咖喎<br />\n好難keep住一直有愛情<br />\n耐咗就會變親情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同佢都係21歲,佢話我知 佢未玩夠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁得啦 應該有第三者</bl